# Learning Reflections README 

## **Developing a responsive footer for a web page using Tailwind CSS**

### Overview
In this project I designed a responsive footer for a web page using Tailwind CSS, which is a utility-first CSS framework. This project utilizes different Tailwind CSS classes.

#### Challenges Faced
The only challenge I faced was adapting to the pre-defined classes.

#### Overall Learning Experience
My learning experience on designing a responsive footer for a web page using Tailwind CSS was interesting and fun! Throughout the development process, I learned new Tailwind CSS classes, and improved my skills. Tailwind CSS actually saves one a lot of time! 

In conclusion, the entire process of this project was an awesome experience and I thoroughly enjoyed completing it. 